  "body": "1. We need to support the account storage redesign.  This should be a configurable `StateDB` class that implements the following structure for accessing account information.\r\n2. [A two-layer account trie inside a single-layer trie](https://ethresear.ch/t/a-two-layer-account-trie-inside-a-single-layer-trie/210)\r\n3. [doc.md](https://github.com/ethereum/sharding/blob/develop/docs/doc.md#two-layer-trie-redesign)\r\n\r\n```python\r\nclass State():\r\n    def __init__(self, state_root, env, db):\r\n        self.state_root, self.env. self.db = state_root, env, db\r\n        cache = {}\r\n        journal = []\r\n\r\n    def get_balance(self, acct):\r\n        key = sha3(acct) + b'\\x00'\r\n        if key not in self.cache:\r\n            self.cache[key] = _trie_get(self.db, self.state_root)\r\n        return self.cache[key]\r\n\r\n    def get_nonce(self, acct): key = sha3(acct) + b'\\x01' ...\r\n\r\n    def get_code(self, acct): key = sha3(acct) + b'\\x02' ...\r\n\r\n    def get_storage(self, acct, k): key = sha3(acct) + b'\\x03' + k ....\r\n```",
